"Visualization_with_AR\"><\/span>Visualization with AR<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Customer experience is the prime concern for any business, and retailers are finding new measures to engage their customers.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">In this realm, one technology that is surmounting obstacles is AR!<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">AR has the potential to offer an incredible user experience, so users don\u2019t have to toggle between trial and return.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">They can visualize a product in a way that was not possible before, and see how the product will look in their house or their wardrobe before making a final call.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Mobile_Shopping\"><\/span>Mobile Shopping&nbsp;<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Mobile shopping is here to stay!<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With technological advancement, consumers choice to shop online has become a ubiquitous reality.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.shopify.com\/enterprise\/mobile-commerce-future-trends\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">According to recent studies<\/span><\/a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, retail mobile shopping, or eCommerce, is expected to reach $728.28 billion by 2025.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">As there is wider usage of mobile devices, eCommerce has become a popular way for people to shop online.&nbsp;<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">This growth in eCommerce can be attributed to the convenience and accessibility it offers consumers.<\/span><\/p>\n<h3><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Alternative_payment_methods_with_Blockchain\"><\/span>Alternative payment methods with Blockchain<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\